@DATABASE "Marauder"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Marauder"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                                 Marauder
                                 ========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35160,175) ZXAMPoke(35161,50) ZXAMPoke(35162,95) ZXAMPoke(35163,250)"}    35160,175:35161,50:35162,95:35163,250
@{"Infinite Smart Bombs" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34225,0)"}    34225,0
@{"All die instantly   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34219,0) ZXAMPoke(34225,0) ZXAMPoke(34230,0)"}    34219,0:34225,0:34230,0
@{"Lives = x           " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(26178,100)"}    26178,x (x= 1-100)
@{"Smart Bombs = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(26183,100)"}    26183,x (x= 1-100)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         The All Die Instantly POKE makes everything blow up
                         as soon as it scrolls into view. Makes the game 
                         UTTERLY pointless!
	                                      Rastan.
@endnode
